Following a work of almost a year, carried out by volunteer developers, supervised by SUN Microsystem, the new Open Office package is shown to the general public with various new features: welcome screen, and the interface reviewed and became less austere, to other more important ones, such as compatibility born for the Apple Mac OS X operating system, and support for the new ODF format (Open Document Format) 1.2, the latest ISO standard version.
