Also interesting, certain functions specific to certain modules, such as the one that allows to reduce the dimensions of PowerPoint presentations, useful for example, to send them by email, or to import PDF files into the graphic development module, keeping the original aspect of the page.
Also on this front, it is possible to create "hybrid PDF" documents that link the typical Adobe format graph to the elements of a spreadsheet or text editor.
